#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:2
#: 1191fd594bff4c7abaefb64e36ff1e15
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:4
#: f4128f6ee9664a28be82307d28ea475f
msgid ""
"A complete 2D Poisson example: define a mesh, write the weak form in pure "
"Python, apply Dirichlet boundary conditions, and solve. The full script is "
"about 30 lines and runs in well under a second on a laptop CPU."
msgstr ""
"一个完整的二维泊松示例：定义网格、用纯 Python 编写弱形式、施加狄利克雷边界条件并求解。完整脚本约 30 行，在笔记本电脑的 CPU "
"上远不到一秒即可运行完毕。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:10
#: 8109cc591be24cfbbc29d7e57af5ab62
msgid "The problem"
msgstr "问题描述"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:12
#: d7bb45e5b4eb4c82a558aa7f99c4eeb2
msgid ""
"Solve the Poisson equation on the unit square :math:`\\Omega = (0, 1)^2` "
"with homogeneous Dirichlet boundary conditions:"
msgstr "在单位正方形 :math:`\\Omega = (0, 1)^2` 上，以齐次狄利克雷边界条件求解泊松方程："

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:15
#: ac16af2048c44eeb88c81894c9da0672
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"-\\Delta u \\;=\\; f \\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u \\;=\\; 0 \\quad \\text{on } \\partial\\Omega."
msgstr ""
"-\\Delta u \\;=\\; f \\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u \\;=\\; 0 \\quad \\text{on } \\partial\\Omega."

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:20
#: 6d13851a4ab8426fb42e787eea345363
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"We pick :math:`f(x, y) = 2\\pi^{2} \\sin(\\pi x)\\sin(\\pi y)` so that the "
"analytical solution is :math:`u(x, y) = \\sin(\\pi x)\\sin(\\pi y)` — handy "
"for sanity-checking the FEM result at the end."
msgstr ""
"我们取 :math:`f(x, y) = 2\\pi^{2} \\sin(\\pi x)\\sin(\\pi y)`\\ ，使得解析解为 "
":math:`u(x, y) = \\sin(\\pi x)\\sin(\\pi y)`——便于在最后对有限元结果进行合理性检验。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:26
#: 519c6f79b78e45f4847a5179a660705e
msgid "The full script"
msgstr "完整脚本"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:66
#: 4fdb7efaca7346aca233bae588c01dfd
msgid ""
"Running this script prints something like ``L2 error: 3.162e-03`` and writes"
" a side-by-side plot of the source term ``f``, the FEM solution, and the "
"analytical solution to ``poisson.png``:"
msgstr ""
"运行此脚本会打印类似 ``L2 error: 3.162e-03`` 的内容，并将源项 ``f``\\ 、有限元解和解析解的并排对比图写入 "
"``poisson.png``\\ ："

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:70
#: d25f70bbcef94811a4be0d1b151e81ca
msgid ""
"Source term f, FEM solution, and analytical solution of the 2D Poisson "
"example"
msgstr "二维泊松示例的源项 f、有限元解和解析解"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:77
#: e0c5d8a7271f43019be0c09ded272a42
msgid "**Running on GPU.** Add a single line after creating the mesh::"
msgstr "**在 GPU 上运行。** 在创建网格之后添加一行代码即可::"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:81
#: a6860acd503e4d788da164a31ea7d2cd
msgid ""
"Every tensor derived from ``mesh`` (assembled matrices, load vectors, the "
"condensed solve) then lives on the GPU automatically — including ``f_vals`` "
"here, since it is built from ``mesh.points``. Only tensors you construct "
"independently of the mesh need to be moved over explicitly, e.g. ``my_tensor"
" = my_tensor.to(mesh.device)``."
msgstr ""
"此后，所有由 ``mesh`` 派生出的张量（装配得到的矩阵、载荷向量、凝聚后的求解）都会自动驻留在 GPU 上——这里的 ``f_vals`` "
"也包括在内，因为它是由 ``mesh.points`` 构建的。只有那些独立于网格而构造的张量才需要显式迁移，例如 ``my_tensor = "
"my_tensor.to(mesh.device)``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:89
#: 1c085919c99a4652a5be3775580ce183
msgid ""
"**Built-in assemblers.** The Laplace and source forms above are common "
"enough that TensorMesh ships ready-made versions "
"(:class:`~tensormesh.LaplaceElementAssembler`, "
":func:`~tensormesh.func_node_assembler`, and others), so you usually don't "
"need to write them by hand. See :ref:`forms-builtins` for the full "
"catalogue."
msgstr ""
"**内置装配器。** 上述拉普拉斯和源项形式十分常见，因此 TensorMesh 提供了现成的版本（\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.LaplaceElementAssembler`\\ 、\\ "
":func:`~tensormesh.func_node_assembler` 等），通常你无需手动编写它们。完整目录请参阅 :ref:`forms-"
"builtins`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:98
#: 9dc911c51ee341c5839682b79380aa80
msgid "Step by step"
msgstr "逐步讲解"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:100
#: 7e5bbbd4aa6d45c9a4bef6bb2932cfdb
msgid ""
"**Mesh.** :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` stores nodes, cells, and any per-node / "
"per-cell data attached to them. :meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_rectangle` "
"produces a triangular mesh of :math:`(0, 1)^2` with target element size "
"``chara_length`` (smaller value → finer mesh)."
msgstr ""
"**网格。** :class:`~tensormesh.Mesh` 存储节点、单元，以及附着其上的任何逐节点／逐单元数据。\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Mesh.gen_rectangle` 会生成 :math:`(0, 1)^2` 的三角形网格，目标单元尺寸为 "
"``chara_length``\\ （值越小→网格越精细）。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:105
#: d4697ad0b8f74da88dc2691ed474bf13
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Weak form.** The two ``forward`` methods are the *only* things you write "
"that depend on the PDE — the library handles assembly. Inside "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler`, the arguments ``gradu``, ``gradv`` "
"are the basis-function gradients already evaluated at every quadrature point"
" of every element; you return the integrand and the library does the rest. "
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` works the same way for vector-valued "
"integrands that depend on per-node data: pass the data via "
"``point_data={...}`` and receive it as a keyword argument with the same "
"name."
msgstr ""
"**弱形式。** 这两个 ``forward`` 方法是你需要编写的、\\ *唯一* 与 PDE 相关的部分——装配由库来处理。在 "
":class:`~tensormesh.ElementAssembler` 内部，参数 ``gradu``\\ 、\\ ``gradv`` "
"是已经在每个单元的每个求积点上求值好的基函数梯度；你只需返回被积函数，其余交由库来完成。\\ "
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` 对依赖于逐节点数据的向量值被积函数采用相同的工作方式：通过 "
"``point_data={...}`` 传入数据，并以同名关键字参数的形式接收它。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:115
#: 9d051e9ad5b247e4ad577190d8adaef0
msgid ""
"**Assembly.** ``Assembler.from_mesh(mesh)()`` returns a "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` (for ``ElementAssembler``) or a "
"torch ``Tensor`` (for ``NodeAssembler``). Internally everything is fused "
"into a single tensorized GPU kernel — no Python-level loop over elements."
msgstr ""
"**装配。** ``Assembler.from_mesh(mesh)()`` 返回一个 "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ （对于 ``ElementAssembler``\\ ）或一个 "
"torch ``Tensor``\\ （对于 ``NodeAssembler``\\ ）。在内部，所有运算都会被融合进单个张量化的 GPU "
"内核——不存在对单元的 Python 层级循环。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:120
#: afb157df07f749c0abd20a28ac82056d
msgid ""
"**Boundary conditions.** :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` applies Dirichlet "
"BCs by *static condensation*: ``condenser(K, b)`` returns a reduced system "
"on the interior DOFs only. After solving the reduced system, "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.recover` glues the inner solution back together"
" with the prescribed boundary values to produce a full-mesh solution."
msgstr ""
"**边界条件。** :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` 通过 *静态凝聚* 来施加狄利克雷边界条件：\\ "
"``condenser(K, b)`` 返回一个仅在内部自由度上的缩减系统。求解缩减系统后，\\ "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.recover` 会将内部解与给定的边界值重新拼合，从而得到整个网格上的解。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:126
#: 9de2b78c9c324ef58f18d98a54ad2c8d
msgid ""
"**Solve.** :meth:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix.solve` dispatches to a "
"sparse solver backend — by default SciPy on CPU and a torch-sla iterative "
"solver on GPU. See :doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers` for the full backend "
"matrix."
msgstr ""
"**求解。** :meth:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix.solve` 会分派到某个稀疏求解器后端——在 CPU "
"上默认使用 SciPy，在 GPU 上默认使用 torch-sla 的迭代求解器。完整的后端矩阵请参阅 "
":doc:`../user_guide/linear_solvers`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart.rst:130
#: d5637608c0e8427d9223d13f9976155f
msgid ""
"**Convergence.** The reported ``L2 error`` should be ``≈ 3e-3`` on the "
"default mesh; halve ``chara_length`` and the error drops by roughly a factor"
" of four — second-order convergence as expected for linear triangles."
msgstr ""
"**收敛性。** 在默认网格上，报告的 ``L2 error`` 应约为 ``≈ 3e-3``\\ ；将 ``chara_length`` "
"减半，误差大致下降为原来的四分之一——这正是线性三角形单元所应有的二阶收敛。"

